data.description: Come see this great 4 bed, large lot on over a third of an acre, with a spacious split-level layout, backed up to a greenbelt and Wonder Wood Park! Upstairs you find 2 bedrooms, and the fully remodeled kitchen, with a dining space that opens to the back deck, overlooking your fully fenced yard with fruit trees! Downstairs has 2 additional rooms, fully remodeled bath, second living space and covered outdoor area leading to the backyard shed, with plenty of room for garden beds and outdoor living--don't forget to check out the secret entrance to the park in the back! So many upgrades, including all new flooring, windows, appliances and new furnace. Come make this home yours, just in time for the holidays! New ROOF at closing!
